doc.after: The United States Coast Guard operates 21 HC 130H aircraft from four bases around the United States  These aircraft are used for search and rescue enforcement of laws and treaties illegal drug interdiction marine environmental protection military readiness International Ice Patrol missions as well as cargo and personnel transport 15
